Class GoReplayPackage

java.lang.Object
com.ontotext.graphdb.replaytool.goreplay.GoReplayPackage
Direct Known Subclasses:

public class GoReplayPackage extends Object
Handles GoReplay package decoding and parsing of the GoReplay header, as well as encoding.
